snippet.textDisplay:
Everything about this collab is just so beautiful ❤ 

The goosebumps from 2:54 got us back to ghar...details like aipan (ऐपण) on the bridge...the infamous Rajula-Malushahi folklore and the flute. 

Every single artist involved did a commendable job in creating this masterpiece. 

Coke studio Bharat and team, Kamla Devi ji, Dig V and Neha Kakkar आप सब्युं कु आभार ईं उत्तराखंडी लोक संस्कृति थै बढावा दींण वास्ता।
